Class Party59

java.lang.Object
geniusweb.party.DefaultParty
geniusweb.exampleparties.skyparty.Party59
All Implemented Interfaces:
geniusweb.connection.Connectable<geniusweb.inform.Inform,​geniusweb.actions.Action>, geniusweb.party.Party, tudelft.utilities.listener.Listener<geniusweb.inform.Inform>
public class Party59
extends geniusweb.party.DefaultParty
A party that places random bids and accepts when it receives an offer with sufficient utility. This party is also a demo on how to support the various protocols, which causes this party to look a bit complex.

parameters

parameters
minPower This value is used as minPower for placed Votes. Default value is 2.
maxPower This value is used as maxPower for placed Votes. Default value is infinity.
